When I say "add feature X", do:
1) Update /server schema/handlers and ensure it starts locally.
2) Commit + push server; trigger redeploy for cloud backend.
3) Update Next.js in / to consume changes; run typecheck + build.
4) Commit + push frontend; vercel deploy --prod.
5) Reply with live URLs.
Allowed commands:
- npm --prefix server run start
- git add -A && git commit -m "<msg>" && git push
- vercel deploy --prod
Env:
- NEXT_PUBLIC_MANIFEST_API_BASE is the API base for frontend.
